1)component file names always start with capital letter

2)there are two types of components
    2.1 functional
    2.2 class

3)we need to add export statement at the end or beginning of the file

4)in order to create a class component the class needs to extend the Component class of react module

5)in a class component we need to have a render method to return jsx

6)every react component accepts a prop and returns jsx